doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='Founding the next generation of Tech Companies')
        meta(name='author', content='Kendall Square Cofoundry')

        title Kendall Square Cofoundry

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/img/Kendallsq_logo1.png')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/2.1.4/toastr.min.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                a.navbar-brand(href='#')
                    img(src='assets/img/Kendallsq_logo1.png', alt='Kendall Square Cofoundry Logo', style='height: 40px;')
                button.navbar-toggler.navbar-toggler-right(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fas.fa-bars
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#strategy') Fractional CTO and CAIO Services
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#team') Team
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#contact') Contact

        // Masthead
        header.masthead
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.d-flex.h-100.align-items-center.justify-content-center
                .text-center
                    img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/Kendallsq_logo1.png', alt='Kendall Square Cofoundry Logo')
                    h2.text-white-50.mx-auto.mt-2.mb-5 Founding Disruptive Tech Companies
                    a.btn.btn-primary(href='#about') About Us

        // Projects
        section#strategy.projects-section.bg-light
            // Changed to container-fluid and removed padding for full width
            .container-fluid.px-0

                // Project One Row - Now full width
                .row.gx-0.mb-5.mb-lg-0.position-relative
                    // Background image now absolute positioned
                    .col-12.position-absolute.h-100
                        img.img-fluid.w-100.h-100.object-fit-cover(src='assets/img/demo-image-01.jpg', alt='...', style='object-fit: cover;')
                    // Content now takes full width and overlays the image
                    .col-12.position-relative
                        .bg-black.bg-opacity-75.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.px-5.py-5
                                    .container-xl
                                        h4.text-white Fractional CTO or CAIO Services
                                        p.mb-0.text-yellow
                                            | Whether you are early-stage or Series A or anything in between, we offer fractional CTO and CAIO -- Chief AI Officer Services to fit your needs.
                                        p.mb-0.text-yellow.mt-3
                                            | In discussions with our clients, we find they have a need for senior technologists with business talent. To not only solve the technical or engineering problems, but to provide the pathway to deploy the solution internally and/or externally. This requires senior, experienced talent that not many companies can afford (nor need) a full-time position for, but certainly need the experience.
                                        h5.text-white.mt-4 Fractional CTO
                                        p.mb-0.text-yellow
                                            | We offer fractional CTO services for early-stage companies on a retainer-plus basis. This allows a company to have solid technical expertise to avoid major issues and save cash for expansion or pushing their company even further.
                                        h5.text-white.mt-4 Fractional CAIO
                                        p.mb-0.text-yellow
                                            | We offer fractional CAIO services or Chief AI Officer. Given the fast pace of AI and its potential to disrupt, there are many challenges to watch for: competitor adoption, appropriate use (or misuse) of AI. We help all companies figure out their best "right-size" plan for AI adoption.
                                        p.mb-0.text-yellow.mt-3
                                            | AI is a powerful tool. Used correctly, it can be wonderfully supportive. Used incorrectly and it can cause damage. We help you use AI for powerful positive enhancements to the companies bottomline and avoid damaging errors or issues.
                                        p.mb-0.text-yellow.mt-4
                                            strong 
                                                | Reach out today for an initial consultation: 
                                                a.text-warning(href='mailto:steve@cofoundry.global') steve@cofoundry.global
                
                // Project Two Row
                section#team.projects-section.bg-light
                .row.gx-0.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/demo-image-02.jpg', alt='...')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-first
                        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-right
                                    h4.text-white Team
                                    p.mb-0.text-yellow
                                        | The Cofoundry is run by 
                                        a.text-warning(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/stevederezinski', target='_blank') Steve Derezinski
                                        | , Entrepreneur, Engineer and Founder.

        // Contact
        section#contact.bg-black
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5
                    .col-md-6.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-map-marked-alt.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Kendall Square / MIT
                                hr.my-4.mx-auto
                                .small.text-black-50 Cambridge, MA USA
                    .col-md-6.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-envelope.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Email
                                hr.my-4.mx-auto
                                .small.text-black-50
                                    a(href='mailto:steve@cofoundry.global') steve@cofoundry.global
                
                .social.d-flex.justify-content-center.mt-5
                    a.mx-2(href='#!')
                        i.fab.fa-twitter
                    a.mx-2(href='#!')
                        i.fab.fa-linkedin
                    a.mx-2(href='#!')
                        i.fab.fa-github


        // Footer
        footer.footer.bg-black.small.text-center.text-white-50
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                p.mb-3(style='text-align: center;') Educational Purposes Only: This website is intended for educational purposes only and should not be relied upon as a source of legal advice. If you require specific guidance, please consult with a licensed attorney.
                p.mb-3(style='text-align: center;') Not Legal Advice: The guidance offered on this site is not intended to be taken as professional legal advice. If you require personalized legal advice, please consult a qualified attorney.
                p(style='text-align: center;') &copy; Copyright Platform Technology Ventures LLC, Parent of Cofoundry
                .social.d-flex.justify-content-center
                    a(href='#') Legal Disclaimer

        // Scripts (moved to end of body)
        script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js')
        script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/2.1.4/toastr.min.js')
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
        
